event.title: was separated from the town of Moncada to be proclaimed a sister municipality 1909

data.event: Colubot Lanat Legaspi Mangandingay Matarannoc Pacpaco Poblacion Salcedo San Agustin San Felipe San Jacinto San Miguel San Narciso San Vicente Santa Maria When the prosperous barrio of San Jose was separated from the town of Moncada to be proclaimed a sister municipality 1909, the inhabitants were jubilant and graceful.
